==Format==
===Group Stage===
*In each game, team with different allies and face off against different opponents.
**All matches are {{abbr/Bo3}}.
***Top 4 players of each group advance to the Playoffs Upper Bracket.
***5th-6th placed players of each group advance to the Playoffs Lower Bracket.
===Playoffs===
*Playoffs Teams are decided by matching everyone with the highest placing available player from the other group that plays a different race (if possible).
*Double-elimination bracket:
**All matches are {{abbr/Bo5}}.
**Finals are {{abbr/Bo7}}.

